These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-4-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, november, february, march
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, eggplant, lemon, nectarine
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, puzzles, chef-climbing, video-games
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, iris, zinnia, tulip
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, librarian, pilot, chef
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, indonesian, brazilian, american
4 different games are played: whist, go, bridge, billiard
 1. the writer is on the far right##1
 2. the person who growsiris is the person eating eggplant##1
 3. the person eating nectarine is the indonesian##1
 4. the brazilian is the person eating eggplant##1
 5. the person playing bridge is between the person playing whist and the person who's hobby is chef-climbing##2
 6. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is the egyptian##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in july is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who growszinnia is the person who's birthday is in november##1
10. the person who's birthday is in february is in an even position##4
11. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
12. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
13. the person eating lemon is on the left of the chef##1
14. the person eating nectarine is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left##1
16. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4
17. the american is on the far left or far right##3
18. the american is the person playing billiard##1
19. the librarian is the person eating blueberry##1
20. the pilot is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
21. the person who growsiris is the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Birthday      | march        | february   | july         | november  |
| Food          | lemon         | eggplant   | blueberry   | nectarine |
| Hobby         | chef-climbing | puzzles    | video-games | drawing   |
| Flower   | amaryllis        | iris  | tulip      | zinnia   |
| Job   | pilot          | chef       | librarian        | writer   |
| Nationality           | american        | brazilian      | egyptian    | indonesian    |
| Game         | billiard | bridge | whist      | go   |

