4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, game, chaman, swisher
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, ice-hockey, skateboarding, volleyball
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, western, drama, crime
 1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 2. the dutch is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
 3. the brazilian is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 5. the person traveling to nizza is the person watching western movies##1
 6. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 7. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
 8. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person who likes emerald##3
 9. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
10. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
11. the person watching sports movies is the italian##1
12. the dutch is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
13. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
14. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
15. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
16. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
17. the malaysian is in an even position##4
18. the game-smoker is the person watching crime movies##1
19. the person playing domino is on the far left or far right##3
20. the person playing poker is in an odd position##4
21. the person traveling to colone is in an odd position##4

