 9. the person traveling to colone is in an odd position##4
10. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
11. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
12. the person playing bridge is the person traveling to venice##1
13. the person traveling to miami is in an even position##4
14. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
15. the person who likes chestnut is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
16. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes green##1
17. the owner of the horse is the person who growslily##1
18. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
